results.name: Partial sums of A252748: a(0) = 0, a(n) = A252748(n) + a(n-1).
link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10000
program: (Scheme, with memoization macro definec) (definec (A252749 n) (if (zero? n) n (+ (A252748 n) (A252749 (- n 1)))))
